review_comments.body:
It might be preferable to do the following instead so as not to leave trailing spaces.

```
chunks->entries[chunk->size - 1].base += 1;
chunk->entries[chunk->size - 1].len -= 1;
```

It _might_ be better to define the logic as a separate function, since you would want to do the same at other parts of the code as well.

